<font color="yellow"><i>[Eun Ha Won]</i></font>

529
00:45:40,047 --> 00:45:44,291
<font color="yellow"><i>Nomor yang Anda tuju sedang sibuk...</i></font>

530
00:45:53,869 --> 00:45:56,969
<font color="yellow">Kenapa dia tidak angkat teleponnya?</font>

531
00:45:57,869 --> 00:46:00,070
<font color="yellow">Apa aku terlalu kasar tadi?</font>

532
00:46:00,070 --> 00:46:02,270
<font color="yellow">Oh, terserahlah!</font>

533
00:46:31,670 --> 00:46:33,969
<font color="yellow">Eun Ha Won.</font>

534
00:46:38,451 --> 00:46:40,369
<font color="yellow">Eun Ha Won!</font>

535
00:47:31,770 --> 00:47:33,770
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu...</font>

536
00:47:36,170 --> 00:47:38,969
<font color="yellow">Kau sebenarnya ingin
melihatnya juga, 'kan?</font>

537
00:47:39,969 --> 00:47:42,969
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu?</font>

538
00:47:42,969 --> 00:47:47,469
<font color="yellow">Maksudku, dia laki-laki
yang dicintai ibumu.</font>

539
00:47:47,469 --> 00:47:49,869
<font color="yellow">Ayahmu.</font>

540
00:47:50,770 --> 00:47:53,170
<font color="yellow">Jangan ikut campur.</font>

541
00:47:57,170 --> 00:48:00,070
<font color="yellow">Datang ke upacara kematian ayahmu.</font>

542
00:48:18,969 --> 00:48:22,170
<font color="yellow">Aku merindukanmu, anakku!</font>

543
00:48:26,369 --> 00:48:27,469
<font color="yellow">Ah, Ibu./
Kenapa?</font>

544
00:48:27,469 --> 00:48:30,869
<font color="yellow">Ibu sudah lama tak berjumpa denganmu,
makanya aku sangat senang melihatmu!</font>

545
00:48:30,869 --> 00:48:33,270
<font color="yellow">Kau harusnya pergi ke hotel saja.
Kenapa datang kesini?</font>

546
00:48:33,270 --> 00:48:36,070
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin melihatmu, jadi aku datang
langsung ke sini dari bandara!</font>

547
00:48:36,670 --> 00:48:38,869
<font color="yellow">Ibu belum berubah sedikit pun!</font>

548
00:48:39,369 --> 00:48:40,469
<font color="yellow">Ayo masuk./
Ayo masuk!</font>

549
00:48:40,469 --> 00:48:41,969
<font color="yellow">Ayo, ayo!</font>

550
00:48:42,969 --> 00:48:48,869
<font color="yellow">Wow, bagaimana anakku
bisa sangat tampan begini?</font>

551
00:48:48,869 --> 00:48:52,170
<font color="yellow">Dan sangat manis?
Dan seksi?</font>

552
00:48:52,170 --> 00:48:54,969
<font color="yellow">Lihatlah Ibu, kau berlebihan lagi!</font>

553
00:48:54,969 --> 00:48:57,070
<font color="yellow">Kenapa?</font>

554
00:48:57,170 --> 00:48:59,469
<font color="yellow">Hentikan, gerah, tahu!</font>

555
00:48:59,469 --> 00:49:00,770
<font color="yellow">Hei, mana bisa kau seperti ini padaku...</font>

556
00:49:00,770 --> 00:49:02,670
<font color="yellow">...padahal aku cuma bisa melihatmu sekali setahun dalam upacara kematian ayahmu?</font>

557
00:49:02,670 --> 00:49:07,070
<font color="yellow">Kali ini, aku akan selalu berada
di dekatmu!</font>

558
00:49:07,070 --> 00:49:10,869
<font color="yellow">Ibu kumat lagi. Aku 'kan sudah menemuimu waktu aku konser di Amerika!</font>

559
00:49:10,869 --> 00:49:11,951
<font color="yellow">Kau anggap itu
pertemuan ibu-anak?</font>

560
00:49:11,951 --> 00:49:14,170
<font color="yellow">Aku cuma melihatmu sebentar
di ruang gantimu!</font>

561
00:49:14,170 --> 00:49:17,070
<font color="yellow">Kali ini, aku akan selalu
jalan-jalan denganmu!</font>

562
00:49:17,969 --> 00:49:19,770
<font color="yellow">Aigoo, lepas!</font>

563
00:49:19,770 --> 00:49:22,469
<font color="yellow">Mau nonton film?
Tidak, kalau teater musikal saja?</font>

564
00:49:22,469 --> 00:49:26,219
<font color="yellow">Tidak jadi! Aku ingin terus
menatap wajah anakku...</font>

565
00:49:26,219 --> 00:49:28,170
<font color="yellow">...jadi kita begadang saja malam ini
dan saling mengobrol!</font>

566
00:49:28,170 --> 00:49:31,869
<font color="yellow">Bu, aku juga ingin begitu,
tapi ada jadwal rekaman besok.</font>

567
00:49:31,869 --> 00:49:33,670
<font color="yellow">Aku harus latihan.</font>

568
00:49:33,670 --> 00:49:37,270
<font color="yellow">Terserah!
Terserah! Terserah!</font>

569
00:49:37,770 --> 00:49:39,770
<font color="yellow">Tunggu, jika kau besok rekaman...</font>

570
00:49:39,770 --> 00:49:42,469
<font color="yellow">....kau takkan ikut
ke upacara kematian ayahmu lagi?</font>

571
00:49:43,869 --> 00:49:46,770
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak mau kesana.</font>

572
00:49:46,770 --> 00:49:50,170
<font color="yellow">Meski aku tidak datang,
Ayah akan tetap ada disini.</font>

573
00:49:51,469 --> 00:49:55,070
<font color="yellow">Ya ampun, anakku sudah dewasa!</font>

574
00:49:55,869 --> 00:49:59,070
<font color="yellow">Tapi tetap saja, kau harus
datang dan melihat Ayah!</font>

575
00:49:59,070 --> 00:50:01,469
<font color="yellow">Ayolah./
Lepas!</font>

576
00:50:01,469 --> 00:50:04,869
<font color="yellow">Ayolah, Seo Woo!
Kau harus datang!</font>

577
00:50:04,869 --> 00:50:08,070
<font color="yellow">Omo. Itu kamar tunangannya Hyun Min?</font>

578
00:50:08,070 --> 00:50:09,969
<font color="yellow">Jadi, mereka berdua
memang akan menikah?</font>

579
00:50:09,969 --> 00:50:12,869
<font color="yellow">Ibu memang berisik sekali ya!</font>

580
00:50:12,869 --> 00:50:15,270
<font color="yellow">Apa Ji Woon sudah
tinggal di rumah ini?</font>

581
00:50:15,770 --> 00:50:16,770
<font color="yellow">Kau sudah datang?</font>

582
00:50:16,770 --> 00:50:20,469
<font color="yellow">Oh, Hyun Min!
Kau masih sama seperti sebelumnya.</font>

583
00:50:21,070 --> 00:50:22,969
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana kabar kakak iparku?</font>

584
00:50:23,570 --> 00:50:25,469
<font color="yellow">Yang kumaksud itu  ibumu.</font>

585
00:50:25,469 --> 00:50:28,070
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau menanyakan itu?</font>

586
00:50:28,070 --> 00:50:30,270
<font color="yellow">Hati-hati di jalan.</font>

587
00:50:34,670 --> 00:50:37,469
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya mereka
bertengkar lagi!</font>

588
00:50:38,070 --> 00:50:40,170
<font color="yellow">Ayo kita pergi, Ibu./
Ya.</font>

589
00:50:53,969 --> 00:50:55,969
<font color="yellow"><i> [Ibu] </i></font>

590
00:51:07,270 --> 00:51:10,469
<font color="yellow"><i>[Ibu: Kau sebaiknya datang besok]</i></font>

591
00:52:04,469 --> 00:52:07,070
<font color="yellow">Baiklah...</font>

592
00:52:07,969 --> 00:52:10,170
<font color="yellow">Bicara apa dia?</font>

593
00:52:16,170 --> 00:52:20,770
<font color="yellow">Aku juga merindukanmu, Ayah..</font>

594
00:53:04,969 --> 00:53:08,469
<font color="yellow">Benarkah?
Aku mendengkur?</font>

595
00:53:08,469 --> 00:53:10,969
<font color="yellow">Ya. Kau juga mengigau.</font>

596
00:53:10,969 --> 00:53:15,270
<font color="yellow">Apa? Aku mengigau apa? Hah?</font>

597
00:53:38,469 --> 00:53:42,770
<font color="yellow">Aku juga merindukanmu, Ayah...</font>

598
00:53:53,070 --> 00:53:54,770
<font color="yellow">Hah?</font>

599
00:53:54,770 --> 00:53:56,170
<font color="yellow">Oh, aku tidak tahu!</font>

600
00:53:58,469 --> 00:54:01,869
<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa besok!
Semoga kau datang!</font>

601
00:54:01,869 --> 00:54:03,770
<font color="yellow">Kubilang jangan main-main
denganku lagi.</font>

602
00:54:03,770 --> 00:54:07,570
<font color="yellow">Hei, jangan buat wajah menakutkan seperti itu!</font>

603
00:54:07,570 --> 00:54:08,969
<font color="yellow">Ya ampun!</font>

604
00:54:09,469 --> 00:54:11,270
<font color="yellow">Hei!</font>

605
00:54:11,270 --> 00:54:13,469
<font color="yellow">Jangan masuk!</font>

606
00:54:14,969 --> 00:54:17,170
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih!</font>

607
00:54:44,770 --> 00:54:46,670
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya kalian berdua
senang-senang ya tadi.</font>

608
00:54:46,670 --> 00:54:49,170
<font color="yellow">Kalian saling tertawa.</font>

609
00:54:49,170 --> 00:54:50,469
<font color="yellow">Apa kalian saling menggoda juga?</font>

610
00:54:50,469 --> 00:54:51,770
<font color="yellow">Urusi urusanmu sendiri.</font>

611
00:54:51,770 --> 00:54:54,270
<font color="yellow">Hei, kau tidak tahu kencan
dilarang di Kediaman Haneul?</font>

612
00:54:54,670 --> 00:54:56,170
<font color="yellow">Terus?</font>

613
00:54:56,670 --> 00:55:00,170
<font color="yellow">Hei, kau tidak bisa begini padaku!
Teganya kau, kau itu tunanganku.</font>

614
00:55:00,170 --> 00:55:02,469
<font color="yellow">Apalagi kau dekat
dengan sepupuku?</font>

615
00:55:02,469 --> 00:55:04,070
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau bersikap seperti ini?</font>

616
00:55:04,070 --> 00:55:05,469
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

617
00:55:05,469 --> 00:55:08,170
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang kita tak punya hubungan apapun,
teman saja bukan.</font>

618
00:55:08,170 --> 00:55:10,070
<font color="yellow">Jadi bukankah ini tidak masuk akal
kau bersikap begini?</font>

619
00:55:12,070 --> 00:55:15,270
<font color="yellow">Tak bisakah kaujelaskan padaku,
supaya aku mengerti?</font>

620
00:55:19,070 --> 00:55:21,670
<font color="yellow">Oh ya.</font>

621
00:55:22,469 --> 00:55:27,770
<font color="yellow">Orang yang tidak ingin
kau lihat adalah ibumu, 'kan?</font>

622
00:55:29,469 --> 00:55:32,915
<font color="yellow">Karena ini bukan hakku, aku takkan menyuruhmu berbaikan dengan ibumu...</font>

623
00:55:32,915 --> 00:55:36,869
<font color="yellow">...atau datang ke
upacara kematian ayahmu.</font>

624
00:55:36,869 --> 00:55:39,070
<font color="yellow">Tapi aku akan berkata
hal ini.</font>

625
00:55:40,770 --> 00:55:44,170
<font color="yellow">Ayahmu pasti sangat kesepian.</font>

626
00:56:17,469 --> 00:56:19,969
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau sebenarnya ingin melihatnya, 'kan?</i></font>

627
00:56:20,070 --> 00:56:23,869
<font color="yellow">Lagipula, dia itu orang
yang dicintai ibumu.</font>

628
00:56:23,869 --> 00:56:25,670
<font color="yellow">Ayahmu.</font>

629
00:57:16,969 --> 00:57:22,570
<font color="yellow">Betapa menyedihkannya pasti mati karena kecelakaan mengerikan setelah membesarkan anaknya sendirian!</font>

630
00:57:22,570 --> 00:57:25,070
<font color="yellow">Apa anak itu bahkan tahu
bagaimana rupa ayahnya?</font>

631
00:57:25,070 --> 00:57:28,869
<font color="yellow">Kau pikir dia akan duduk di sana sendirian seperti itu jika dia tahu ayahnya?</font>

632
00:57:28,869 --> 00:57:32,969
<font color="yellow">Sudah jelas ayahnya menghamili ibunya
dan lepas tanggung jawab!</font>

